# =============================================================================
# 自定义钩子说明:
#
# 1. pre-commit: 检查大文件(>1MB)和行尾空格
# 2. pre-push: 运行快速测试套件
# 3. commit-msg: 验证消息格式
#
# 安装方式:
#   cp .git/hooks/pre-commit .git/hooks/pre-commit.sample
#   chmod +x .git/hooks/pre-commit
#
# =============================================================================
